('a0d6f60d-ece4-40f8-aca2-955b4abc5d88', '56948fec-ce3d-493b-afc4-4e281e9b8f58', 3, 'Decent tool overall, but the mobile layout could use improvement for tablet users.', true, (timestamp '2026-04-21 09:00:00' + interval '5 hours 37 minutes')),
